<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.2/css/all.css"
          integrity="sha384-vSIIfh2YWi9wW0r9iZe7RJPrKwp6bG+s9QZMoITbCckVJqGCCRhc+ccxNcdpHuYu" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../static/css/common.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
<!--sidebar-->
<div class="sidebar">
    <!-- todo change to mustache -->
    <a href="03_Main.html"><img src="img/tsis.png" class="logo"/></a>
    <ul class="sidebar_ul">
        <li>
            <a href="RecommendationEduPage.mustache">주제별 강좌 보기</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="SubjectEduPage.mustache">카테고리별 교육 검색</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="AcademyEduPage.mustache">기관별 교육 검색</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="SelectEduPage.mustache">교육기관</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="LegendEduPage.mustache">카테고리</a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="AdminMainPage.mustache">관리자</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
<!--/sidebar-->

<!--content-->
<div class="content">
    <!--header-->
    <header>
        <div class="login-info">
            <span>죠르디님 환영합니다!</span>
            <button type="button" class="logout"><a href="IndexPage.mustache">로그아웃</a></button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <!--header-->

    <!--section-->
    <section>
        <header class="subject-purple-header">
            <div class="subject-purple-header__select">
                <div class="subject-purple-header__select__item">
                    <span class="subject-top-note">원하시는 주제를 선택해 주세요</span>
                    <div class="subject-option">
                        <select class="subject-option__large">
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="subject-purple-header__select__item">
                    <div class="subject-option">
                        <select class="subject-option__medium">
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="subject-purple-header__select__item">
                    <div class="subject-option">
                        <select class="subject-option__small">
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="subject-purple-header__select__item">
                    <span class="subject-top-note">과정의 수준을 선택해 주세요</span>
                    <div class="subject-option">
                        <div class="subject-option__level">
                            <div class="subject-option__level--advanced">
                                <input type="checkbox">
                                <label>전문과정</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="subject-option__level--basic">
                                <input type="checkbox">
                                <label>기본과정</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="subject-option__level--elective">
                                <input type="checkbox">
                                <label>선택과정</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="subject-notice-bar">
            <div class="subject-notice-bar-icon">
                <img class="subject-icon-sm" src="../../../static/img/star.svg"> : 베스트강좌
                <img class="subject-icon-sm" src="../../../static/img/full-heart.png"> : 관심강좌
            </div>
            <div>
                <img class="subject-icon-sm" src="../../../static/img/help.svg">
                <span>
                        <a href="LegendEduPage.mustache">
                            어떤 주제를 선택해야 할지 모르겠다면? 카테고리를 참고해 보세요(클릭)
                        </a>
                    </span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <ul class="subject-result">
            <li class="subject-result__title"></li>
            <li class="subject-result__column">
                <div></div>
                <div></div>
                <span>No.</span>
                <span class="subject-result__column--course-name">강좌명</span>
                <span class="subject-result__column--academy-name">기관명</span>
                <span class="subject-result__column--is-online">온라인/오프라인</span>
                <span>위치</span>
                <span>상세보기</span>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="subject-pagination">
            <div>
                <img class="subject-icon-sm" src="../../../static/img/left-arrow.png">
            </div>
            <ul class="subject-pagination__number">
            </ul>
            <div>
                <img class="subject-icon-sm" src="../../../static/img/right-arrow.png">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--/section-->

    <!--footer-->
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-info">
            <div>
                <p>문의처</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>교육담당자 | 인사팀 정병석 과장</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <!--/footer-->
</div>
<!--content-->
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../../static/js/SubjectEdu.js"></script>
</body>

</html>